			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The two key spells are Dooming Darkness at 29 (snare) and Invoke Fear at 34, with an honorable mention to Call of Bones (34).
<br />

<br />
However, you can still fear kite very well below that level, but I don't find it quite as cost effective, as the mana cost of Fear is high relative to your mana pool, and your regen sucks still.
<br />

<br />
In a lot of situations at higher levels you will still pick Fear over Invoke Fear, and use higher aggro spells to "yo yo" kite fearable mobs in relatively small spaces.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
	</tr>
