				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The real fun begins when you get to solo Hate tier 4 named casters.  They root your pet, snare you, you you begin to run in fear.  
<br />

<br />
Basically the mob fear kites you!
<br />

<br />
Anyway, I soloed M-Gem 4 and the 3rd one for a choice in my ranged slot.
<br />

<br />
Have fun with you necro, I know many who regained a love for the game with their necro.
