				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I'm a new necro player and I started fear kiting at 4th when I got the spells to do it now at 12th I'm doing it with a temp in Paludal Caverns on the bandits for 14-15% XP/kill, for example yesterday I dropped a couple of the higher level bandits at the same time with my pet on one, me DoTing both and lifetapping the one I was on, isn't too hard finished mine with 12% mana from 54% and sat down while the pet took out a bit more of the other one and the DoT's wore off, I had the pet back off and I finished with a Lifedraw.  (Thats was an aggro kite btw)
